{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"slideshow_CtnG98":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_bW6A4P":{"type":"slide","settings":{"background":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2000x560_-_Chevy_2500_-_Cypress_gray_NB2_7d244830-a2b0-489f-9ced-77731e2a52da.png","image_overlay_opacity":0,"content_position":"center","text_alignment":"center","text_color":"#000000","title":"","heading_size":"h2","heading_color":"","subheading":"","description":"","desc_size":"text-desc-base","button_text_1":"","button_link_1":"","button_style_1":"btn--primary","button_size_1":"","button_text_2":"","button_link_2":"","button_style_2":"btn--primary","button_size_2":""}}},"block_order":["slide_bW6A4P"],"name":"t:sections.slideshow.name","settings":{"container":"container-full","slideshow_height":"adapt","show_dots":false,"show_nav":false,"autoplay":false,"autorotate_speed":3,"pagination_background":"light","controls_position":"center","pagination_style":"dots","show_text_below":false,"text_alignment_mobile":"center","accessibility_info":"Slideshow about our brand","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","enable_bg_zoom_effect":false}},"jump_links_UeawGp":{"type":"jump-links","blocks":{"link_C8imG8":{"type":"link","settings":{"label":"GVM Packages","target_id":"gvmpackages"}},"link_y9rErk":{"type":"link","settings":{"label":"GVM Specification","target_id":"gvmspecification"}},"link_AGYMRH":{"type":"link","settings":{"label":"Approved Wheels","target_id":"approved-wheels"}},"link_8FKHCp":{"type":"link","settings":{"label":"Suspension Collection","target_id":"suspensioncollection"}},"link_KmD9dx":{"type":"link","settings":{"label":"GVM Experts","target_id":"gvmexperts"}}},"block_order":["link_C8imG8","link_y9rErk","link_AGYMRH","link_8FKHCp","link_KmD9dx"],"name":"Jump links","settings":{"container_mode":"full","container_width":"1200","bg_color":"#ffffff","text_color":"#111111","hover_color":"#111111","active_color":"#111111","border_color":"#0000001f","pad_y":10,"offset":0,"duration":650}},"rich_text_GbXVUF":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_XhCLHT":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Build the Ultimate Beast:  Chevy Silverado 2500HD Super-Truck Packages 2020 - 2026<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":true,"heading_size":"h1","heading_color":"#5683c2"}},"text_CfcJd4":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Shatter your payload limits and command the outback without compromise with a Silverado 2500 GVM upgrade. Offroad Industries (ORI) delivers Australia’s ultimate, fully Federally Approved GVM upgrades for the Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD range. Our SSM approvals only apply to GMSV Vehicles. We cannot do private imports.<\/p><p><strong>The ORI Advantage:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Massive Stance<\/strong>: Options ranging from a sleek 3” lift up to our monster 6.5” package on 37” tyres.<\/li><li><strong>NB2 Upgrades Made Easy<\/strong>: A seamless, ORI-approved pathway from NB1 to the heavy-duty NB2 category via VTA-065187 or we can upgrade NB2 to NB2 via our VTA-065796<\/li><li><strong>Bulletproof Compliance<\/strong>: Rigorously tested and backed by Federal SSM Certification.<\/li><\/ul><p><br\/><\/p><p>Backed by punishing testing and uncompromising Federal SSM Certification, an ORI GVM Package doesn't just upgrade your Silverado; it takes it to true \"Super-Truck\" status. Operating under exclusive ORI Vehicle SSM Approvals, we provide a streamlined, zero-headache pathway to reclassify your rig from an NB1 to a heavy-hitting NB2 category.<\/p><p>The result? Your fully loaded truck, all your gear, and that 4.5T trailer in tow are 100% compliant, secure, and road-legal nationwide when completed Pre-Rego (Federal). Why not invest in your brand new Chevy Silverado 2500HD now? <\/p><p><\/p><p><strong>*Please note that some workshops may apply additional discretionary administration fees to the quoted installation and engineering price. Additionally, all Post-Registration GVM upgrades will incur additional local fees. Shipping is not included in the price.<\/strong><\/p><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_XhCLHT","text_CfcJd4"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"rich_text_PtmRiF":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_mpxUJy":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"ORI FEDERALLY APPROVED GVM PACKAGES","highlight_style":"underline","enable_highlight_text_color":true,"heading_size":"h1","heading_color":"#5683c2"}}},"block_order":["heading_mpxUJy"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"gvmpackages","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_WcaAiR":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_JVKNjL":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 1: $16,500* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_f9G7kD":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 1: The Weekender Family Getaway<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_fRRw7g":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The perfect entry point for a legal payload boost and an aggressive stance.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 5500kg (Approx. 1708kg payload) | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> 3\" Lift with Fox 2.5 HTO Performance Series Shocks, ORI 500kg heavy-duty leaf packs, heavy-duty BDS Control Arms, and Husky Extenda Flares.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> The family tourer needing a higher payload while keeping the truck 100% legal and safe.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> Achieve a lifted, commanding stance with premium USA-made shocks. This setup upgrades your vehicle to an NB2 category, significantly improving stability under load while safely retaining its full 4.5T towing capacity<\/li><li><strong>Part Number: <\/strong>CHV-2500-Stage1-GVM<br\/><\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_JVKNjL","heading_f9G7kD","text_fRRw7g"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_1_5500_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_pR9RXR":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_nNBqbG":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 2: $22,500* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_dHpa9y":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 2: The Tourer Edition (Lapping Australia)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_eiTTm6":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Increased strength and a massive payload upgrade utilizing Fox 2.5 DSC suspension & BDS components.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg (Approx. 2198kg payload) | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> 3\" Lift with Fox 2.5 DSC Performance Elite Series Suspension, ORI 500kg heavy-duty leaf packs, heavy-duty BDS Control Arms, and Husky Extenda Flares. Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> 4WD tourers driving long distances on corrugated roads, heavily loaded with a bull bar and high tow-ball weight. Perfect for maximizing off-road performance and load capacity.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> The DSC adjustability allows you to \"dial in\" your ride—stiffen it for the highway and soften it for the tracks with the simple turn of a knob. All while delivering an incredible 6000kg GVM limit.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage2-GVM<br\/><br\/><\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_nNBqbG","heading_dHpa9y","text_eiTTm6"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_2_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_M8ykcj":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_p3JeNT":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 3: $27,500* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_KMefdY":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 3: The Heavy Hauler (Super Comfort Mode)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_aVwiWh":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The ultimate comfort from your Chevy Silverado 2500HD with our fully engineered BDS Coil-Over Edition.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg (Approx. 2190kg payload) | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> 3\" Lift BDS Coil-Over Conversion, Fox 2.5 DSC Performance Elite Series Shocks, ORI 500kg leaf packs, and heavy-duty BDS Control Arms. Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Fully built rigs with tray\/canopy setups that also tow 4.5T and require heavy ball weights.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> A massive payload increase that transforms the Silverado 2500HD into a true heavy-duty platform. The front Coil-Over conversion provides unparalleled ride quality and front-end control, legally supporting huge weight without sacrificing comfort.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage3-GVM<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_p3JeNT","heading_KMefdY","text_aVwiWh"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_3_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_VKJ6aN":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_AtKMTT":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 3.5: $48,500* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_fFTkhn":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 3.5: The Heavy Hauler (Kelderman Air Edition)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_NGC7ym":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The ultimate in load-carrying flexibility. We ditch the leaf springs for Kelderman full rear air suspension.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg (Approx. 2190kg payload) | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> 3\" Lift BDS Coil-Over Conversion, Fox 2.5 DSC Performance Elite Series Shocks, and heavy-duty BDS Control Arms. <strong>Upgraded<\/strong> with Kelderman fully adjustable rear air suspension (replacing the heavy-duty leaf packs). Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Fully built rigs with changing rear loads, heavy canopies, and massive tow ball weights.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> You get the unparalleled front-end ride quality of the Coil-Over conversion, paired with the ultimate flexibility of Kelderman rear air. Easily raise or lower the rear end of your Chevy Silverado to perfectly match your load, keeping your truck level, comfortable, and highly capable.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage3-GVM-K<br\/><br\/><\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_AtKMTT","heading_fFTkhn","text_NGC7ym"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_3.5_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_rJkhtG":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_DWKAtN":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 4 : $28,000* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_R6xiqM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 4: The 5-Inch Lift Build<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_YBjh6X":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>A lifted stance with a massive GVM, engineered for 37” Tyres.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> BDS 5” Suspension Package, heavy-duty BDS Control Arms, and ORI 550kg leaf packs. Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> The hardcore enthusiast who demands a significantly lifted stance and a higher-than-normal GVM while remaining fully legal and compliant.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> The 5” BDS package allows for larger 37\" tyres without straining the torsion bar setup. This ensures a smoother ride and massive ground clearance. Completed Pre-Rego under our SSM, your truck is 100% federally approved and legal.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage4-GVM<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_DWKAtN","heading_R6xiqM","text_YBjh6X"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_4_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_giCQLF":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_GUEKJN":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 5: $28,000* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_GqENUg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 5: The \"Lifted & Loaded\" (6.5-Inch Lift)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_ddpBQL":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>When 5 inches isn't enough, let's go to 6.5. 100% legal Australia-wide (Pre-Rego only).<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Elite with BDS Lift Kit Technology (6.5-Inch Suspension Lift), and ORI 500kg heavy-duty leaf packs.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> Enthusiasts who want the functionality of a huge GVM and maximum legal payload, while retaining a 4.5T towing capacity and a massive on-road presence. Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> The Stage 5 kit is federally recognized under our SSM approval. Because it is available Pre-Rego only, you can drive your heavily lifted truck in any state, feeling safe, fully insured, and completely legal while looking the part.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage5-GVM<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_GUEKJN","heading_GqENUg","text_ddpBQL"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_5_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_zgLfNt":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_KF8CC3":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 6 : $34,000* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_eDyjtL":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 6: The \"MEGA \" Build (6.5-Inch BDS Coilover <\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_aW8UUa":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>Ever wondered how these monsters get around legally? ORI Stage 6 makes the dream a reality.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Elite with BDS Lift Kit Technology (6.5-Inch Coil-Over Suspension Lift engineered for up to 37\" Tyres), and ORI 500kg heavy-duty leaf packs. Engineered for up to 37” Tyres.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> The absolute hardcore enthusiast who demands a monster of a truck that still delivers heavy-duty NB2 payload limits and 4.5T towing capacity.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> Fully engineered for ultimate comfort and control. Equipped with a 6.5” BDS Coil-Over lift kit, this setup is 100% legal Australia-wide exclusively via ORI's Pre-Rego packages under our SSM approval. Drive anywhere knowing your monster build is completely legal and safe.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage6-GVM<br\/><\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_KF8CC3","heading_eDyjtL","text_aW8UUa"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_6_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"left","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"image_with_text_9MGF8c":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_b3w7Fn":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"Stage 6.5 : $53,000* - Installed & Engineered"}},"heading_gDQyxC":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Stage 6.5: The \"Monster\" Kelderman Build (6.5-Inch Lift)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2"}},"text_Ktnecb":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><em>The undisputed King of the Off-Road. Front Coil-Over performance meets Kelderman 4-Link rear air suspension.<\/em><\/p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:<\/strong> 6000kg | <strong>GCM:<\/strong> 12,474kg<\/li><li><strong>Key Features:<\/strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Elite with BDS Lift Kit Technology (6.5-Inch Coil-Over Suspension Lift engineered for up to 37\" Tyres), featuring a <strong>Kelderman 4-Link full air rear suspension setup<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Best For:<\/strong> The ultimate enthusiast who demands Super Tourer status without compromise.<\/li><li><strong>Benefit:<\/strong> This is the absolute pinnacle of suspension engineering. Combining the benefit of a BDS Coil-Over front end with the payload flexibility of a Kelderman 4-Link rear air setup, this package makes the ultimate dream a reality. 100% federally approved Pre-Rego, safe, insured, and ready to dominate any terrain in total luxury.<\/li><li><strong>Part Number:<\/strong> CHV-2500-Stage6-GVM-K<br\/><\/li><\/ul><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["subheading_b3w7Fn","heading_gDQyxC","text_Ktnecb"],"name":"t:sections.image-with-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/stage_6.5_5900_gvm_SILVERADO_2500HD.png","image_width":"50%","image_position":"right","vertical_alignment":"center","column_gap":"medium","row_gap":"medium","padding_left":0,"padding_right":0,"align_content_container":"none","mobile_padding_left":15,"mobile_padding_right":15,"padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"padding_top_mobile":60,"padding_bottom_mobile":60,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"rich_text_RV8dqr":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_g3UJNm":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h2>Silverado 2500 GVM Upgrade Options for Enhanced Towing Power<\/h2><p>One of the biggest challenges when you’re heading off the beaten track or out to a jobsite is making sure you can take all your gear, without overloading the manufacturer payload. When you want to be able to tow your trailer, boat, caravan, or simply load up the tub with more tools, you need some serious capabilities that won’t impact the structure or safety of your Chevy. <\/p><p>Our range of upgrades spans a huge scope of specs, giving you something custom, road-safe, and anywhere up to a 198% payload increase. Haul more and go further while still maintaining all the things you love about your truck when you get an engineered and installed Silverado GVM upgrade. <\/p><h2>Chevrolet Silverado 2500HD GVM Upgrades for Maximum Performance<\/h2><p>If you own a Chevy, you already know they’re an impressive beast both on and off the road. When you want to not only maintain their performance, but maximise it, Silverado GVM upgrades can help get you there. Between the boosted wheelbase from upgraded <a href=\"https:\/\/www.offroadindustries.com.au\/collections\/suspension\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">suspension<\/span><\/a>, to more structural support from the new shocks and control arms, you’ll get better ground clearance, improved traction, and a structurally sound setup. These upgrades mean that you can carry your gear without strain - even on tough terrain. <\/p><p>When you transform your truck with a GVM package from ORI, you’ll also be able to add other upgrades that enhance the utility, functionality and personality of your vehicle. Get a fresh set of wheels to match the hauling power you’ve got, add on new <a href=\"https:\/\/www.offroadindustries.com.au\/collections\/bushwacker\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">fender flares<\/span><\/a> to keep the undercarriage of your truck clear from dirt, or install a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.offroadindustries.com.au\/collections\/titan-fuel-tanks\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">long range fuel tank<\/span><\/a> so you can go further. Silverado GVM upgrades do more than give you greater hauling power, they open you up to a whole new way to drive and enhance your truck. <\/p><p><\/p><h2>Silverado GVM Upgrade Packages – Enhance Your Vehicle’s Off-Road Capability<\/h2><p>When you’re offroading, sometimes you have to make a choice between taking all the gear you want with you or sticking to an easier path. If you’re too overloaded, handling, control, and stability can be impacted - but all of these concerns are alleviated with carefully engineered and installed <a href=\"https:\/\/www.offroadindustries.com.au\/pages\/ori-gvm-upgrades\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">GVM upgrades<\/span><\/a>. <\/p><p>Our range enables you to lift your ground clearance by up to 6.5 inches, making it easier to tackle rugged tracks, beat your own path through the terrain, and maintain the traction you want. <\/p><h2>Silverado 2500 GVM Upgrade – Strengthen Your Vehicle for Heavy Duty Use<\/h2><p>Aside from the occasions when you need to be hauling higher loads, a GVM upgrade with ORI gives you a more resilient, hard-wearing truck regardless of what you’re carrying. You can tackle tough ground more easily, get through dry or soggy conditions with greater ease, and maintain a smooth ride no matter where you go and how much you’ve got in the tub. <\/p><p>No matter what motivates you, how you like to drive, or what you demand from your truck, a Chevy Silverado 2500HD GVM upgrade from ORI offers you the driving experience you’ve always wanted. Explore the range now, and if you’re unsure which option is right for you, you can contact us for a personal recommendation. <\/p><p>After you’ve purchased your upgrade, you can get everything installed and engineered and discover the difference it’ll make to your Chevy in a real-world environment. No matter whether you’re driving for work or play, you can head off with confidence knowing your Silverado can handle everything without compromising the handling, comfort, and control you’re used to. <\/p><p><\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_g3UJNm"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"center","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"collapsible_tabs_UDrTRf":{"type":"collapsible-tabs","blocks":{"content_aq3BG8":{"type":"content","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"What is a GVM upgrade and why do I need one?","content":"<p>Gross Vehicle Mass (GVM) is the maximum your Silverado can legally weigh when fully loaded—including the truck, passengers, fuel, accessories (like bull bars and canopies), and tow ball weight. If you are towing heavy or building a touring rig, the factory payload gets eaten up fast. Our GVM upgrades legally increase this limit so you can carry your gear without voiding your insurance or risking hefty fines.<\/p>","custom_liquid":"","content_page":"","open":false}},"content_97RYwd":{"type":"content","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"What does \"Pre-Rego\" and \"SSM Approval\" mean?","content":"<p>SSM stands for Second Stage of Manufacture. When we upgrade your truck <em>before<\/em> it is registered for the very first time (Pre-Rego), the federal government recognizes ORI as the secondary manufacturer. This means your massive lift, larger tyres, and upgraded GVM are baked into the truck's federal compliance plate. It is 100% legal to drive and insure in every state and territory in Australia.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","custom_liquid":"","content_page":"","open":false}},"content_k7yrdM":{"type":"content","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Will upgrading my GVM reduce my towing capacity?","content":"<p>Not with an ORI package. Some GVM upgrades force you to sacrifice towing capacity to carry more weight in the tub. Our Silverado 2500HD packages retain your factory 12,474kg GCM (Gross Combination Mass), meaning you keep your full 4.5T braked towing capacity while maximizing your truck's payload.<\/p>","custom_liquid":"","content_page":"","open":false}},"content_xFACmJ":{"type":"content","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"What does the NB1 to NB2 category upgrade mean?","content":"<p>By federal standards, NB1 vehicles are \"Light Goods Vehicles\" (under 4.5 tonnes). Our SSM packages legally reclassify your Silverado 2500HD as an NB2 \"Medium Goods Vehicle\" (over 4.5 tonnes). This reclassification is the secret to legally unlocking that massive 5500kg–6000kg GVM.<\/p>","custom_liquid":"","content_page":"","open":false}},"content_rQQeBN":{"type":"content","settings":{"icon":"none","title":"Are 35-inch and 37-inch tyres actually legal on these builds?","content":"<p>Yes! If done Pre-Rego through our Stage 4, 5, 6, or 6.5 SSM packages, the larger tyre sizes are federally engineered and certified as part of the build. No state-based engineering headaches—just turn the key and drive your monster truck legally anywhere in the country.<\/p>","custom_liquid":"","content_page":"","open":false}}},"block_order":["content_aq3BG8","content_97RYwd","content_k7yrdM","content_xFACmJ","content_rQQeBN"],"name":"Collapsible tabs","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","section_header_padding_bottom":"medium","section_header_content_spacing":"medium","heading":"<strong>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)<\/strong>","highlight_style":"none","enable_highlight_text_color":false,"heading_size":"h2","heading_color":"","subheading":"","description":"","item_heading_font":"body","item_heading_size":"h6","column_gap":"medium","content_width":"full","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"faqs","custom_class":"","animations":"inherit"}},"rich_text_rnLAPH":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_YjLxhA":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Chevrolet Silverado 2500 LTZ GVM Specifications","highlight_style":"underline","enable_highlight_text_color":true,"heading_size":"h1","heading_color":"#5683c2"}}},"block_order":["heading_YjLxhA"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"container":"container","color_schema":"","text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":40,"show_section_divider":false,"divider_width":"container","custom_id":"gvmspecification","custom_class":"","anim